From: Tuxbox Build System <build@tuxbox.org>
Date: Sun, 22 Dec 2024 12:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] pam_namespace: add missing includes for uClibc

uClibc requires explicit inclusion of locale.h for setlocale/LC_COLLATE
and libgen.h for dirname. glibc may provide these transitively, but
uClibc does not.

Fixes compilation errors:
- 'LC_COLLATE' undeclared
- implicit declaration of function 'dirname'
- implicit declaration of function 'setlocale'

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [uClibc-specific]
Signed-off-by: Tuxbox Build System <build@tuxbox.org>

---
 modules/pam_namespace/pam_namespace.h | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/modules/pam_namespace/pam_namespace.h b/modules/pam_namespace/pam_namespace.h
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/modules/pam_namespace/pam_namespace.h
+++ b/modules/pam_namespace/pam_namespace.h
@@ -54,6 +54,8 @@
 #include <fcntl.h>
 #include <sched.h>
 #include <glob.h>
+#include <locale.h>
+#include <libgen.h>
 #include "security/pam_modules.h"
 #include "security/pam_modutil.h"
 #include "security/pam_ext.h"
--
2.34.1
